Actually, before opening this star block, if I move these keys over here out of the way first, I can save a tiny bit of time with this star.

Good, no screw ups with that turn block this time. I should be able to make it with time to spare.
Huh. There were four smiley coins total here. Maybe that's to give you some leeway in case you accidentally destroy one. But, the level would probably become unwinnable if you destroyed two or more.
That's two good coins deposited into the safety deposit box. Now I just need one more.
World 1 Boss - Reimu Hakurei (Normal)
